  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Dialog: Function-Block: Linear-Motion</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Linear-Motion FB </para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-Add-FBLinearMotion">Add Linear-Motion FB</link></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="VariableName">default</text> motion-values at the output from the <text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion FB</text> are equal to the <text styleclass="Interface">Master-Machine-Angle</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> (MMA). </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use the output from the <text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion FB</text> as the machine-angle at the input of other <text styleclass="VariableName">Kinematic FBs</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text>&#32;</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Use the <text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion dialog-box</text> to edit the output relative to the <text styleclass="Interface">Master-Machine-Angle</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" style="text-indent:-18px; margin-left:18px;">Open Linear-Motion dialog-box</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:40px; border-right:none;">
          <para styleclass="Interface" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-Icon-FB-LinearMotion.png" scale="100.00%" padding="0 2 0 0" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="border-left:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Edit the<text styleclass="Element"> Linear-Motion FB</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets">Double-click the </text><text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text Howindent4bullets"> in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text><text styleclass="VariableName">. </text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="VariableName-IT">- or -</para>
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-How-to-Open-a-Dialog-Box" styleclass="SeeAlso">How to Open a Dialog-Box</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion FB dialog-box</text> is now open.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Linear-Motion dialog-box</para>
