          <para styleclass="Interface2">or</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName">If </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Accumulate</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="VariableName">: Output = (Revs × 360) + Master Machine Angle +</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header"> Start-Angle</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text><image src="Red-14-1.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="VariableName" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
